                'questionText' => 'What are some common tropes in science fiction?',
                'answerText' => 'Science fiction frequently deals with the nature of humanity, asking questions about when or if a computer can achieve consciousness, the existence of other sentient alien species, and humanity\'s origins. Sometimes these entities, that is, robots, computers, and aliens, are presented as monstrous mirrors of our own tendencies.

