            0 => [
                'questionText' => 'What are some examples of political intrigue in media?',
                'answerText' => 'Game of Thrones and the Song of Ice and Fire books are probably the most popular examples! Other television shows like House of Cards and The West Wing are modern political intrigue. The Dune book and film series are all about political maneuvering and machinations of power, and The Poppy War is a more recent book in this tradition. The Crusader Kings series and games like it are probably the best example of dynastic political intrigue video games.',
