                'questionText' => 'What are the tropes of futuristic media?',
                'answerText' => 'Highly advanced technology, often so advanced it\'s beyond modern explanation or understanding. Faster-than-light travel, perfect virtual reality, matter creation, artificial intelligence and robots, cold fusion, and other technological wonders. Often futuristic stories explore the implications of such technology, its social consequences, or the differences in the way the haves and have-nots access it.',
