Futuristic settings are also quite popular in video games; in fact, games like Cyberpunk 2077 and Citizen Sleeper are both based on tabletop roleplaying games! Other popular games like Halo and Mass Effect project a spacefaring future for humanity, while Horizon Zero Dawn, Bioshock, and Fallout offer a bleaker vision.',
